fasta_path = None
generator = FastaProteinBatchGenerator(fasta_path, seq_length=600, seed=42)
params = generator.get_params()
expect1 = {'fasta_path': None, 'seed': 42, 'seq_length': 600, 'shuffle': True}
assert params == expect1, params
assert generator.n_bases == 20, generator.n_bases
cloned_generator = clone(generator)
generator.close()
